of what it is they're doing.

00:16:51.700 --> 00:16:53.250
I, I truly believe that.

00:16:53.250 --> 00:16:56.850
And when you look at great media works through
the ages, they were always accomplished by

00:16:56.850 --> 00:17:01.240
visionaries, not people with focus groups
and not people that were looking at search

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:03.000
engine optimizers, ok?

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:05.579
It was somebody who decided I'm gonna do this
and they did it.

00:17:05.579 --> 00:17:09.400
And if people follow them, fanstinkintastic,
you get to do more of that.

00:17:09.400 --> 00:17:11.579
That's your reward is you get to keep working.

00:17:11.579 --> 00:17:14.630
And if you get some cash and prizes along
the way, ok.

00:17:14.630 --> 00:17:20.100
So the danger with social media is that once
you start engaging in that, you're from the

00:17:20.100 --> 00:17:22.750
South, you must remember the, the story of
the Tar Baby.

00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:23.750
Remember your Brer Rabbit?

00:17:23.750 --> 00:17:24.959
&gt;&gt;male #3: Actually I'm from California.

00:17:24.959 --> 00:17:26.949
&gt;&gt;Alton Brown: Do you remember your Uncle
Remus stories?

00:17:26.949 --> 00:17:31.559
Yeah, they're not really politically correct
anymore but the truth is, is, is social media

00:17:31.559 --> 00:17:34.850
is the Tar Baby, once you stick your finger
in it, once you poke it you're pretty much

00:17:34.850 --> 00:17:36.180
caught up in it.

00:17:36.180 --> 00:17:41.470
And it's very easy to then start letting that
influx of information, that influx of opinion,

00:17:41.470 --> 00:17:45.760
that influx of emotion from all around kind
of infect what it is you're doing.

00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:49.380
And so that's why a lot of celebrities have
other people do it for them and they never

00:17:49.380 --> 00:17:51.330
touch it at all.

00:17:51.330 --> 00:17:56.929
Or you've got people that do it a lot, but
don't do it in a way where they really let

00:17:56.929 --> 00:17:58.770
people, they put a lot out, but don't let
a lot in.

00:17:58.770 --> 00:18:02.830
