you know.

00:18:02.830 --> 00:18:06.940
And I've spent some time looking at what other
celebrities do, real cele, like big-time celebrities,

00:18:06.940 --> 00:18:11.880
not just cablelebrities like me, but what
big celebrities do on, on places like Facebook

00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:15.520
is they basically just put, they share out.

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:20.801
And, and I think that's, I mean that's fine,
but I tend to want to also see what's, what's

00:18:20.801 --> 00:18:21.801
coming in.

00:18:21.801 --> 00:18:23.020
