actually I, I, I realize that social media

00:18:42.210 --> 00:18:46.270
is actually going to allow me to work better
because what it's going to allow me is to

00:18:46.270 --> 00:18:51.920
focus my future work, more and more on the
stuff that I wanna do that I feel confident

00:18:51.920 --> 00:18:56.280
my real fan base will also enjoy and will
allow me connectivity to them to allow them

00:18:56.280 --> 00:18:57.970
to know what it is I'm doing.

00:18:57.970 --> 00:19:02.490
So in other words I'm gonna be able to preach
louder to a smaller choir if that makes any

00:19:02.490 --> 00:19:03.490
sense.

00:19:03.490 --> 00:19:05.870
And that's one of the things that when you,
when you do TV projects, if you're just on

00:19:05.870 --> 00:19:10.120
a network then you're, you're, it's a shotgun
and it's, and it's always going out there

00:19:10.120 --> 00:19:12.450
and you always have to assume that somebody's
watching it.

00:19:12.450 --> 00:19:15.990
