&gt;&gt;Jeff Freburg: Do you cook with your daughter
often?

00:33:24.030 --> 00:33:25.260
&gt;&gt;Alton Brown: Do I cook for her often?

00:33:25.260 --> 00:33:26.260
Everyday.

00:33:26.260 --> 00:33:27.260
&gt;&gt;Jeff Freburg: With her.

