00:34:31.809 --> 00:34:32.809
&gt;&gt;male #4: Ok.

00:34:32.809 --> 00:34:36.849
&gt;&gt;Alton Brown: I have never looked for a restaurant
on using a computer, so unless it's a map

00:34:36.849 --> 00:34:37.849
function.

00:34:37.849 --> 00:34:41.049
I'm standing here in Missoula, Montana, where's
the closest food?

00:34:41.049 --> 00:34:42.049
I will do that.

00:34:42.049 --> 00:34:47.089
I will use the map function on my iPhone for
