how the heck do I search for recipes on the

00:36:58.000 --> 00:36:59.000
internet?

00:36:59.000 --> 00:37:04.530
And my, my answer is basically you, you, you
don't unless you're looking for something

00:37:04.530 --> 00:37:06.430
very, very specific with a name attached to
it.

00:37:06.430 --> 00:37:11.029
