cross reference ingredient lists or time that
it takes or reviews and then offer up another

00:37:51.759 --> 00:37:55.089
ten elsewhere on the internet based on if
you like this one.

00:37:55.089 --> 00:37:59.880
I think that could work, but then you, you've
that's some pretty sophisticated integration.

